  <summary date="2023-10-10T14:31:08Z" status="Introduced in House">Small Business Child Care Investment Act

This bill deems certain nonprofit child care providers to be small business concerns so that they may participate in specified loan programs administered by the Small Business Administration (e.g., the 7(a) loan program).</summary>
